TLS Anomaly Detection with JA3 + Zeek
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand JA3 fingerprinting fundamentals for TLS traffic analysis
Configure Zeek network security monitor for TLS monitoring
Implement JA3-based anomaly detection mechanisms
Create automated Python scripts for TLS anomaly alerting
Analyze TLS traffic patterns to identify security threats
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of TLS/SSL protocols
Linux command line proficiency
Python programming fundamentals
Network security concepts knowledge
Experience with log analysis
